      <title>部长称瑞银资本要求应适度</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-capital-requirements-should-be-proportionate-minister-says-2024-12-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士财政部长卡琳·凯勒-苏特 (Karin Keller-Sutter) 表示，新银行法规对瑞银设定的资本要求应该“相称”，因为瑞士试图在金融业竞争力和保护纳税人之间取得平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-capital-requirements-should-be-proportionate-minister-says-2024-12-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 14:55:37 GMT</pubDate>
